15 pages, 5 eps figures; Invited Talk at DARK 2007, Sydney,
  Australia, 23-28 Sept 2007; WSPC-Proceedings, MPLA (Special Issue);
  references added

column11:
  We construct $B$-function of the Hermitian symmetric space
$\OO(n,2)/\OO(n)\times \OO(2)$ or equivalently of the tube $(Re z_0)^2> (Re
z_1)^2+...+ (Re z_n)^2$ in $C^{n+1}
